import { Grid } from '@material-ui/core';
import React from 'react'
import Navbar from '../components/Navigation/Navbar.js';
import '../styles/Home.css';
import Footer from '../components/Footer/Footer.js';
import { makeStyles } from '@material-ui/core/styles';
import E_Board from '../components/TeamCards/E_board';
import Director from '../components/TeamCards/Director';
import VP from '../components/TeamCards/VP';
import Tech_Team from '../components/TeamCards/Tech_Team';

const useStyles = makeStyles({
    root: {
        backgroundColor: 'rgb(175, 217, 228)',
    }
});
function Team() {
    const classes=useStyles();
    return (
        <Grid container direction="column" className={classes.root}>
            <Grid item>
                <Navbar/>
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                Founders
            </Grid>
            <Grid item container>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={1} />
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={12} >
                    <E_Board />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={1} />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                Directors
            </Grid>
            <Grid item container>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} >
                    <Director />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                Vice-Presidents
            </Grid>
            <Grid item container>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} >
                    <VP />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                Tech-Team
            </Grid>
            <Grid item container>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
                <Grid item xs={12} sm={8} >
                    <Tech_Team />
                </Grid>
                <Grid item xs={0} sm={2} />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item>
                <Footer/>
            </Grid>
        </Grid>
    )
}

export default Team
